<br />Unless i am misunderstanding what you are telling me, i believe i am.
<br />
<br />I have the NMI set to trigger on VBlank, where it is incremented. 
<br />
<br />Other then that, i push the registers onto the stack, then run the next note from the embedded NSF file, then pull the registers back off the stack, and return from interrupt.</div>

